simulation.statement: The daily profit range increased from $287.11 - $315.81 to $300.18 - $342.40. We expect a 6.57% increase in profit margin after menu engineering.

base.statement: We can expect daily profit to range from $287.11 to $315.81 with an average of $301.46.

adjusted.statement: We can expect daily profit to range from $300.18 to $342.40 with an average of $321.29. This represents a projected 6.57% increase in profit margin after menu engineering.

parameters: Profit per item of Plow Horses (popular but low profit margin) increased by 10%
assumptions: Monte Carlo simulation uses 90 days of transactions data
All customers who would have bought the dropped items will buy the remaining items
The popularity of Plow Horses would remain the same despite the price increase
